node.text: Okay, this was one of the funnest moments I’ve ever had in my life. This is a completely original song and video, and I felt “Like a Boss”! This movie is a must-see. Discover why critics are calling #LikeABossMovie “laugh out loud hilarious”! Get ready to 😂 with @TiffanyHaddish, @fullyRoseByrne, and @SalmaHayek! Reserve tickets 🎟️ now to see it FIRST at Girls’ Night Out advance screenings tomorrow, in theatres everywhere Friday. #ad

node.text: Props to the girls who put together looks, take time to get the picture, and post them. I did it for 10 minutes and was over it. I’m much better at taking selfies in bed with my grey velvet headboard as the backdrop and sending it straight to the story.

node.text: Ocean, Gigi (O’s grandmama) and I took a trip to Newport Beach for a few days to see our family friends. I had to post this sweet moment of Ocean and her best friend Hazel. Hazel’s mama, Olivia, and I have been best friends for 30 years (yes, our entire lives), and our mama’s have been the same since Jr. High- 3 generations. Liv and I have pictures together as babies we always look back on, and now our girls will have the same. Kisses to that 😘
